{"tid":238461,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【日圓走勢】沽Yen買Bitcoin 日圓兌港元挑戰6.7算","createTime":"2017-05-11T04:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T04:38:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80320eb483e3e823a096dcc6b8e8577b49a8a7e7","tid":238461,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pNpMyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pNpMyp.jpg&h=cba1cccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日圓資金繼續流向美元及虛擬貨幣，除了炒高Bitcoin，日股連日上揚，美元兌日圓再升穿114水平，最新報114.32；每百日圓兌港元更由6.85跌至6.81，有望跌穿6.8算。<br />\n<br />\n日經平均指數再升0.2%，最新報19,937點。<br />\n<br />\nbitcoin今日最高曾見1,750美元，目前報1,739美元，仍然企穩1,700美元大關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678518&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678518%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1cc91e3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56678518%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&h=46415ccf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56678518&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511</a>"}]}